{"tid":1392784,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"律政司 Big Boss 係董建華 [集思]","createTime":"2019-08-01T00:44:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-17T18:09:11.000Z","uid":269761,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"06a1ea681ca415a42a3d42779982d76ed3e14610","tid":1392784,"uid":269761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T00:44:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">作為70 後和理非，睇多少少香港歷史。我認為律政司單嘢，老董有角色～！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0wRq2Fw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0wRq2Fw.png&h=cc857b0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">如果心水清嘅都知道林鄭、鄭若驊都係董伯推上去嘅。<br />\n</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kdDQunc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkdDQunc.png&h=757c8513&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">777唔洗講，鄭若驊幫老董搞國際仲裁，法律研究深得老董愛護，袁國強下馬，立即補上。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LMXhTPu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLMXhTPu.png&h=4fb388f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">律政司刑事檢控科「一群檢控人員」撰寫匿名公開指責鄭若驊，又話受到政治干預，我諗要值得從老董入手查。</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Bdwq2M4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBdwq2M4.png&h=6b9c31c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">老董牽頭嘅<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">團結香港基金</span></span>2014年成立，回應當時佔領運動，同好多掛羊頭嘅基金一樣，幫中央搞宣傳，實制係推動中央政策，如<span style=\"color: purple;\">大灣區、明日大嶼</span>，劉華之前宣傳人工島，架空發展局、土地大辯論，成績有目共睹。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XdFZ7fc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXdFZ7fc.png&h=4c468822&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">[black]董建華噚日仲講外國勢力，我諗如果有外國勢力，小朋友嘅防具應該唔只咁，仲要無飯食，仆街。老董緊貼中央，之前搞通識，之後推國史教育中心，內容親共。教育改革令家長學生無所適從，老董有好大責任。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n[/black]</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9dchTZD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9dchTZD.png&h=ac665fb2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">何志平被美國法院入罪，老董作為前上師，無寫求情信，你以為佢傻？係明白北京心意。<br />\n<br />\n曾經話腳痛下台，如今老而不退，戀棧權位做政協副主席。揀人管治香港政府，架空政府政策正是他！Big Boss 董建華。</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n連登仔，我地有咩可以做？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2be0d3f62ee5d4edfa29ba9d9044e2550433353","tid":1392784,"uid":269761,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T00:57:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">好多人想搞鄭若驊老公潘樂陶，但好明顯佢兩個有名無實，我認為無意義，否則大家應該叫</span><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">潘鄭若驊</span>！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">團結香港基金理事盛智文噚個人贊成獨立調查，我諗傳媒、個人應該追擊基金成員。俾機會佢地『團結』香港人，繼而瓦解哩個基金會。</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jaLGBmA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjaLGBmA.png&h=bde26faf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有無得諗？</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n團結香港基金理事<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ourhkfoundation.org.hk/zh-hant/node/37\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ourhkfoundation.org.hk%2Fzh-hant%2Fnode%2F37&d=puaUx2dgpXXsrsLU9noyGMyZng7V5AOcQmv89xdKlzQ%3D&h=0ac7a6b4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ourhkfoundation.org.hk/zh-hant/node/37</a>"},{"pid":"b63d40ddcf114ccb8f77d7190e3e99902f61ed79","tid":1392784,"uid":89184,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T00:57:55.000Z","msg":"幾時死"},{"pid":"b7b9d022526de4ecc5088368284062ae8b6053b9","tid":1392784,"uid":82640,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T00:58:50.000Z","msg":"認同"},{"pid":"6fb9e88d6374ff882a2dc69946a78a9ad9448186","tid":1392784,"uid":269221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T00:59:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c3ce7088228fd33833b4d31d913e005f69776b3b","tid":1392784,"uid":13174,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T01:00:50.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"59ae20f03fab71cbeec5ddaff28f07a2c7066dc7","tid":1392784,"uid":106336,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T01:01:15.000Z","msg":"呢條撚屌由22年前已經搞壞香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46694bee63876bd01ec85cb2ef14a6cf0e4c2206","tid":1392784,"uid":238013,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T01:04:57.000Z","msg":"老而不死"},{"pid":"646eec21a15304091f57f484e06939548de8a790","tid":1392784,"uid":269761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T01:09:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">順帶一題，2016年，董建華响灣仔會展，用香港國際仲裁中心名義幫中國解決同菲律賓嘅南海爭議，鄭若驊係主席，此前無咩人識佢，連政府中人都唔識，老董推佢俾777，一上就做律政司。<br />\n </span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W9aWqhr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW9aWqhr.png&h=183e896b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/kknews.cc/zh-hk/world/o94kbo.amp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Famp%2Fs%2Fkknews.cc%2Fzh-hk%2Fworld%2Fo94kbo.amp&d=puaUx2dgpXXsrsLU9noyGMyZng7V5AOcQmv89xdKlzQ%3D&h=7a50601d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/kknews.cc/zh-hk/world/o94kbo.amp</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">而鄭本身有無共產黨背景？要靠大家查～<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"20214561d013548e5be1a38559e5e8ca9df95a5e","tid":1392784,"uid":44980,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T01:12:03.000Z","msg":"何志平真係慘一個人受晒<br />\n佢老細仲可以日日9up"},{"pid":"cf460b299056978a3b61e8d84d62a714f7d08c5f","tid":1392784,"uid":55010,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T01:18:46.000Z","msg":"方向正確，5年前就覺得得基金好鬼，團咩結成日都搭把口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bb4d89e6878c70abc09d725fc7293cecc765958","tid":1392784,"uid":246118,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T01:20:53.000Z","msg":"依條死老嘢幾撚時死？港版慈禧"},{"pid":"a5b7bc696eacf66c94f4b91c11c88c3f325582d8","tid":1392784,"uid":61281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T01:23:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"10b906033e958e620c3159ddfe0b43c08283f236","tid":1392784,"uid":60410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T17:16:14.000Z","msg":"值得一推"},{"pid":"a6d85b1bc6e2b38228b91b134ff967c6fcf0c870","tid":1392784,"uid":60410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T18:06:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b542b1022e0f8fd5405828d2b586a3960c93fb8d","tid":1392784,"uid":22624,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T18:09:11.000Z","msg":"呢條仆街害港害足咁多年"}]}